trend_summary: Sequential images show a stable, curvilinear suburb. Built-up footprint changes little; only scattered infill lots, a revamped school/sports complex and a few new roadside commercial pads arise. Two storm-water ponds appear in the south. Tree canopy steadily thickens, giving the area a greener, more mature look.
notable_changes: Creation of two retention ponds in the southern neighbourhood between mid-series and final image.
Expansion and resurfacing of the western school/sports campus, including new athletic fields.
Scattered infill housing on previously vacant residential lots throughout the map.
Small commercial pads or parking expansions along the northern arterial road.
Overall increase in tree canopy and lawn cover, indicating landscape maturation and greening.
